item.description: You have so much more motivation than I do! I couldn’t think of a list that big, let alone actually do it ;p I try so hard to keep my site updated I couldn’t imagine trying to do 52 things. But I’m sure you’ll do gra!eaThtt’s an amazing painting. I can’t do anything like that at all. I wish I was half as talented ;oMy boyfriend and I try to go to different restaurants, but there isn’t many in our town. I think maybe only 10 or 15, and most of them are fast food. Boooo.
